  "body": "I use Mist to manage my wallets. I put my computer in sleep mode, and wakes it up after a while again. As expected, the blockchain can be far behind at this point.\n\nAlmost always, there are 0 peers and no synchronization can be started. I waited for several minutes, and it did not improve.\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/2412342/13201603/46196af2-d879-11e5-9c35-ad6fed98a44f.png)\n\nHowever, restarting Mist, and thus restarting geth, quickly found peers and started to synchronize.\n",
