    "body": "Ok, got the error now, but where can I find the logs?\n\nI am on Windows.\n\nThe output from geth itself simply stopped when I paused Windows, and did not start again. So the last lines show:\n\n```\nI0226 22:38:41.787742   10784 blockchain.go:1243] imported 1 block(s) (0 queued 0 ignored) including 1 txs in 5.5035ms. #1065038 [40df9243 / 40df9243]\nI0226 22:38:55.942523   10784 blockchain.go:1243] imported 1 block(s) (0 queued 0 ignored) including 0 txs in 3.5022ms. #1065039 [164c192a / 164c192a]\nI0226 22:39:16.176947   10784 blockchain.go:1243] imported 1 block(s) (0 queued 0 ignored) including 1 txs in 5.0033ms. #1065040 [2632be30 / 2632be30]\n```\n\nWhen I am writing this, Mist shows 0 peers and the current block should be 1067822. I have waited for approx one hour for any peer to be found.\n",
